{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop arms sales and any military support to Ukraine and Israel.",
        "additional_details": "We believe every penny spent on death and destruction should have otherwise been invested in hospitals schools and public services. Money it seems, can always be found for wars.\r\n\r\nWe believe that stopping war funding and redirecting money home, will improve our country. We think citizens are taxed, without having enough control over state spending and that it is more beneficial for the UK public to reap the benefits of their contributions, than funding what we see as foreign adventurism.",
        "background": "We demand the government cease all arms sales to these countries along with any military support. We believe we should end our part in the pain and destruction inflicted by war, and that we should not support weapons but instead, invest the money in our own citizens and services.",
